436
00:49:11.869 --> 00:49:13.620
You are perfectly safe.

437
00:49:14.663 --> 00:49:16.707
- Okay.
- Your life is your own.

438
00:49:17.541 --> 00:49:18.917
Please know that.

439
00:49:19.001 --> 00:49:21.712
Your well-being
is of utmost importance to us.

440
00:49:22.337 --> 00:49:23.338
Okay.

441
00:49:24.214 --> 00:49:25.549
Completely up to you. of course.

442
00:49:25.632 --> 00:49:28.802
but you might want to stick close to home
for the next few days.

443
00:49:28.886 --> 00:49:32.764
We've a lot to clean up.
and it may be distressing for you to see.

444
00:49:32.848 --> 00:49:35.601
But we will put things right.

445
00:49:35.684 --> 00:49:39.479
To that end. if we may be of assistance
with Helen's remains…

446
00:49:39.563 --> 00:49:40.939
- Nope.
- Okay.

447
00:49:41.607 --> 00:49:43.984
If we can help you in any way
please let us know.

448
00:49:44.067 --> 00:49:48.405
We can deliver food. medicine.
whatever you need.

449
00:49:48.488 --> 00:49:50.407
Just dial zero. day or night.

450
00:49:50.490 --> 00:49:54.828
You will want to call from a landline
as all the cellular networks are down.

451
00:49:54.912 --> 00:49:56.872
But we are here for you.

452
00:50:00.876 --> 00:50:03.962
We feel like we're doing
all the talking here.

453
00:50:05.088 --> 00:50:07.591
Are there any questions
you might have for us. Carol?

454
00:50:07.674 --> 00:50:08.800
Anything at all.

455
00:50:14.306 --> 00:50:16.475
Yeah. Yeah. sure.

456
00:50:17.893 --> 00:50:19.520
I guess to start with.

457
00:50:20.354 --> 00:50:23.815
what the fuck is happening?

458
00:50:23.899 --> 00:50:25.275
Well. basically…

459
00:50:25.359 --> 00:50:26.777
It's an alien invasion. right?

460
00:50:26.860 --> 00:50:28.695
I mean. obviously it's an alien invasion.

461
00:50:28.779 --> 00:50:30.155
Actually. no. It is not.

462
00:50:30.239 --> 00:50:33.033
What the fuck it isn't. You know my name.

463
00:50:33.116 --> 00:50:35.577
You know Helen's name.

464
00:50:35.661 --> 00:50:39.248
You are talking to me from my TV!

465
00:50:39.831 --> 00:50:43.168
And what the fuck is with everybody's…

466
00:50:43.252 --> 00:50:44.545
Shit like this…

467
00:50:44.628 --> 00:50:48.298
And those two weird…
the weird neighbor kids next door.

468
00:50:48.382 --> 00:50:49.842
They know where some goddamn key…

469
00:50:50.425 --> 00:50:53.679
How would they know that. huh?

470
00:50:53.762 --> 00:50:57.182
- Are you reading my mind?
- No. Absolutely not.

471
00:50:57.266 --> 00:50:58.934
We couldn't do that if we wanted to.

472
00:50:59.017 --> 00:51:01.562
Who is "we?"
Why is everybody suddenly "we?"

473
00:51:01.645 --> 00:51:04.523
You know. we could continue this
after you've had a good night's sleep.

474
00:51:04.606 --> 00:51:06.692
Who is "we?"

475
00:51:06.775 --> 00:51:08.986
"We" is us. Just us.

476
00:51:09.069 --> 00:51:10.070
Who the fuck is "us?"

477
00:51:10.153 --> 00:51:12.948
Us. There are no aliens.

478
00:51:13.615 --> 00:51:15.075
Not on this planet.

479
00:51:15.158 --> 00:51:20.414
We are. however. beneficiaries
of extraterrestrial technology.

480
00:51:20.497 --> 00:51:23.292
Fourteen months ago.
astronomers discovered a radio signal

481
00:51:23.375 --> 00:51:25.669
from 600 light-years away.

482
00:51:26.253 --> 00:51:27.880
There's no telling
how long it's been repeating.

483
00:51:27.963 --> 00:51:30.591
Maybe throughout all of human existence.

484
00:51:31.300 --> 00:51:34.303
This signal. it's made up of four tones

485
00:51:34.386 --> 00:51:39.349
representing guanine. uracil.
adenine and cytosine.

486
00:51:40.058 --> 00:51:43.437
It's a recipe. it turns out.
for a nucleotide sequence.

487
00:51:44.021 --> 00:51:45.147
RNA.

488
00:51:46.148 --> 00:51:48.859
Scientists have created
this sequence in a lab.

489
00:51:48.942 --> 00:51:53.864
It is not a living thing. per se.
It is more akin to a virus.

490
00:51:53.947 --> 00:51:55.824
Though it's not that exactly either.

491
00:51:56.909 --> 00:52:01.246
It's kind of a psychic glue
capable of binding us all together.

492
00:52:03.165 --> 00:52:04.166
Okay.

493
00:52:05.459 --> 00:52:06.877
So. if you're not aliens…

494
00:52:08.837 --> 00:52:10.464
Who am I talking to right now?
Who are you?

495
00:52:11.340 --> 00:52:13.258
This particular individual?

496
00:52:13.342 --> 00:52:14.968
This is Davis Taffler.

497
00:52:15.052 --> 00:52:19.389
Under Secretary of Agriculture
for Farm Production and Conservation.

498
00:52:20.265 --> 00:52:23.936
But you are currently
talking to every person on Earth.

499
00:52:24.019 --> 00:52:25.771
including Davis Taffler.

500
00:52:26.396 --> 00:52:27.397
We're all one.

501
00:52:27.981 --> 00:52:29.274
How does that work?

502
00:52:30.025 --> 00:52:32.653
We don't know exactly. It just does.

503
00:52:34.571 --> 00:52:35.948
Can I talk to the President?

504
00:52:36.031 --> 00:52:39.034
That individual passed away this evening.
unfortunately.

505
00:52:39.117 --> 00:52:43.330
Along with quite a few senior members
of the United States government.

506
00:52:43.413 --> 00:52:48.335
Davis Taffler happened to be
nearby and intact.

507
00:52:48.418 --> 00:52:49.962
And he was wearing a suit. So…

508
00:52:50.045 --> 00:52:52.631
So. you're in charge now?

509
00:52:52.714 --> 00:52:54.466
- The Under Secretary of…
