510
00:52:54.550 --> 00:52:57.511
Nobody's in charge.
Or everybody's in charge.

511
00:52:58.095 --> 00:52:59.888
Really. there's no such thing anymore.

512
00:52:59.972 --> 00:53:02.891
But there's got to be others like me.

513
00:53:02.975 --> 00:53:05.310
Your situation is a rare one.

514
00:53:05.394 --> 00:53:08.647
