11 other individuals like yourself.

515
00:53:08.730 --> 00:53:10.107
In Albuquerque?

516
00:53:10.190 --> 00:53:12.317
No. In the world.

517
00:53:12.818 --> 00:53:14.236
We have reached out to them.

518
00:53:14.736 --> 00:53:17.948
Like you. they are disoriented.
Understandably.

519
00:53:19.825 --> 00:53:21.368
Rest assured. Carol.

520
00:53:21.451 --> 00:53:24.162
We will figure out
